{"tid":2051841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部讚賞國際各方理解支持中方","createTime":"2020-06-05T05:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T05:30:59.000Z","uid":42188,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"763ef511c39582a48c777d8222336c33ef8a6596","tid":2051841,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"中國外交部發言人中國人趙立堅4日在例行記者會上説，中方<span style=\"color: red;\">對國際上各方理解支持中方涉港有關立場和行動表示讚賞</span>，敦促<span style=\"color: red;\">個別國家</span>摒棄意識形態偏見，摘掉有色眼鏡，客觀、公正看待中方有關決定及立法，不以任何方式插手幹預中國香港事務和中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n有記者問：中國全國人大推進中國香港維護國家安全立法的舉措在<span style=\"color: red;\">一些西方國家</span>引發了質疑，但<span style=\"color: red;\">也有不少國家公開表態支持中方</span>有關舉措，認為這是維護國家主權、安全、發展利益的正義之舉，有助於中國香港保持繁榮穩定，任何外部勢力無權幹涉。中方對此有何評論？<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅説，中國香港回歸以來，&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;&ldquo;港人治港&rdquo;、高度自治方針得到切實貫徹落實，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國香港居民享有的各項權利和自由依法得到充分保障，國際社會對此已有公論</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不少國家 = 北韓、斯里蘭卡、緬甸、菲律賓、敘利亞、坦桑尼亞、布隆迪及烏干達<br />\n<br />\n個別國家 = 其他200幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"bb50561dd24642de864b31055d87327b54207f1e","tid":2051841,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"講大話既最高境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔止呃人地，仲要呃埋自己"},{"pid":"18238c2f8bc3eab769946ebb12a2c994603cd32c","tid":2051841,"uid":280020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"講完就解決完件事<br />\n非常出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe492d40bc8bdd7cd74086c3e96fa2ff4e554f0","tid":2051841,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18238c2f8bc3eab769946ebb12a2c994603cd32c","tid":2051841,"uid":280020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"講完就解決完件事<br />\n非常出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港人港地：K.O. !</span></span>"}]}